DESCRIPTION:Event Types: Community\,Hobbies\,Sports/Recreation\,Training -C
	lasses/Workshops\n\nNeighborhoods: Central Area/Squire Park\n\nSponsoring 
	Organization: LANGSTON\n\nContact: Jahi McGhee\n\nContact Phone: 206684475
	8\n\nContact Email: langston.institute@seattle.gov\n\nAudience: All\n\nPre
	-Register: Yes\n\nCost: Free\n\nLink: https://www.langstonseattle.org/prog
	rams/karate-with-tyron/\n\nTyron Asphy\, founder of Japan-American Butokuk
	an Karate Association\, has returned to the Langston Hughes Performing Art
	s Institute\, where he taught community karate classes over 40 years ago.\
	n\nTyron works with five instructors to offer martial arts classes to stud
	ents ages 5 to 75 years old. His commitment to bringing access to discipli
	ne\, flexibility\, and self-defense to the Black youth and other residents
	 in the Central District area is invaluable to the overall health and well
	-being of our community.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/
	learn-at-langston-karate-with-tyron/18448015/2026-03-30T00\n\nFrom SEAtoda
